# Gameplay Mechanics Rules

## Combat System
- Turn-based combat
- Text-based actions via OpenAI
- Monster AI with cooldowns
- Status effects and buffs

## Character System
- Profession-based abilities
- Experience and leveling
- Stat progression
- Customization options

## Ability System
- Cooldown management
- Mana cost system
- Effect types:
  - Damage
  - Healing
  - Status effects
  - Buffs/debuffs

## Map System
- AR-based location tracking
- Monster spawns
- Treasure locations
- Distance calculations
